---
const services = [
  { label: 'bizmote Top', href: '/' },
  { label: 'bizFlag', href: '/flag/' },
  { label: 'bizShip', href: '/ship/' },
  { label: 'bizLab', href: '/lab/' },
  { label: 'Notes', href: '/notes/' },
  { label: 'Contact', href: '/contact/' },
];

---

<footer class="border-t border-tankai bg-white px-6 py-12 md:px-12 md:py-16 xl:px-16">
  <div class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-[1120px] gap-11 md:grid-cols-[minmax(240px,1fr)_minmax(420px,1fr)]">
    <div>
      <a class="inline-block font-cormorant text-[34px] leading-none outline-none transition-opacity hover:opacity-70 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sumi focus-visible:ring-offset-4" href="/">
        bizmote
      </a>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-md text-noukai">
        BtoB企業のGTM支援、起業家コミュニティ、AI実装ラボを通じて、挑戦が市場に届く仕組みをつくります。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-noukai">SITE</div>
        <div class="mt-3 grid gap-2.5 font-mono text-xs">
          {services.map((link) => <a class="outline-none transition-colors hover:text-noukai focus-visible:text-noukai" href={link.href}>{link.label}</a>)}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-noukai">LEGAL</div>
        <div class="mt-3 grid gap-2.5 font-mono text-xs">
          <a class="outline-none transition-colors hover:text-noukai focus-visible:text-noukai" href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-4 font-mono text-[11px] text-noukai md:col-span-2">
      <span>© bizmote Inc.</span>
      <span>Tokyo, Japan</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
